snippet.title: What is Footium
snippet.description:
Footium is a play-to-earn online football management game. Footium Clubs allow you to become an Owner, Manager and Scout of a Metaverse Football team. Climb the leagues and compete in cups to win prizes by being a savvy spender, mastermind tactician and having a great eye for talent.

Twitter: https://twitter.com/footium_game
Discord: https://discord.gg/footium
